distanceTo

public double distanceTo(Location location,
                         int mode)
Returns the distance between the object the method is called by and the location thats passed in. It can use pythagoras (flat surface) or a mode that includes the earth radius into it's calculation (sphere).

Parameters:
location - Location to be meassured against
mode - The selected mode
Returns:
Distance in km
Throws:
IllegalArgumentsException
